# My Skills

Personal collection of dev skills for [Codex (OpenAI)](https://github.com/openai/codex) and [Claude Code (Anthropic)](https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code), distilled from daily practice.

All skills follow统一命名规范，详见 [NAMING.md](./NAMING.md)。

## Skills

| Skill | 分类 | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| [ko-dx-rca](./ko-dx-rca/) | Developer Experience | 根因分析 (5-Why methodology) |
| [ko-kb-html](./ko-kb-html/) | Knowledge Base | 为 plan、architecture、PRD、prototype、review、research、report 等长文档生成自包含 HTML companion |

## Usage

### Claude Code

```bash
claude mcp add-skill /path/to/myskills/ko-dx-rca
claude mcp add-skill /path/to/myskills/ko-kb-html
```

### Codex

Copy the skill's `SKILL.md` content into your Codex agent instructions or reference it via project config.

For always-on HTML companions, add this global agent instruction after installing or copying `ko-kb-html`:

```markdown
When you produce a substantial Markdown document such as a plan, architecture doc, PRD, prototype spec, review, research note, report, postmortem, or implementation brief, use `ko-kb-html` to create a self-contained `.html` companion when the document has enough structure to benefit from layout, navigation, diagrams, comparison, or interaction, unless the user explicitly asks for Markdown only.
```

## Creating a New Skill

```bash
# 1. 创建目录（必须遵循 ko-{分类}-{功能} 格式）
mkdir ko-dx-newskill

# 2. 从模板创建 SKILL.md
cp SKILL_TEMPLATE.md ko-dx-newskill/SKILL.md

# 3. 编辑 SKILL.md，确保 name 与目录名一致
```

命名规则详见 [NAMING.md](./NAMING.md)。

## Structure

```
myskills/
├── AGENTS.md              # Agent instructions
├── README
├── NAMING.md              # 命名规范（必读）
├── SKILL_TEMPLATE.md      # Skill 模板
├── evals/
│   └── evals.json         # Skill pressure scenarios
├── index.md               # Directory index
├── ko-dx-rca/
│   └── SKILL.md
├── ko-kb-html/
│   ├── SKILL.md
│   └── references/
│       └── html-quality-targets.md
└── ko-{分类}-{功能}/
    └── SKILL.md
```
